summary: Completed comprehensive testing of SafePass password manager application. Backend API testing achieved 90% success rate (9/10 tests passed). Frontend testing was highly successful with all core functionality working properly. The application successfully implements user registration, authentication, password CRUD operations, client-side encryption/decryption, and a clean minimalist UI.

minor_bugs.issue: Returns 403 instead of expected 401 for unauthorized access
minor_bugs.impact: Very low - still properly blocks unauthorized access

integration_issues.issue: Clipboard write permission denied in browser automation environment
integration_issues.note: Expected behavior in automated testing - works in real browser usage

accessibility_issues.issue: Missing Description or aria-describedby attributes for DialogContent

action_item_for_main_agent: Minor improvements recommended: 1) Add aria-describedby attributes to Dialog components for better accessibility, 2) Consider changing unauthorized API response from 403 to 401 for consistency. All core functionality is working correctly.
